[INFO] 2024-01-18 16:48:29,385 | judge.views:73 | {'start_time': datetime.datetime(2024, 1, 18, 8, 48, 29, 370827, tzinfo=<UTC>), 'action_id': 16, 'action_name': 'Windows Simple Hardening', 'team_id': 6, 'team_name': 'team4', 'answer': b"$defender = Get-MpPreference\r\n$defender.DisableRealtimeMonitoring = $false\r\n$defender | Set-MpPreference\r\n(gwmi -list win32_shadowcopy).Create('C:\\','ClientAccessible')"}
